 opportunities to learn from the best in the industry- through webinars, workshops, leadership meets to help you get ahead in the game of life.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id class="brz-columns brz-css-nvbqf brz-css-idcwn" data-custom-id="jsmjdejulowufzaooaahsutlfdcwmoccggvi"><div class="brz-bg brz-css-kjasd"><div class="brz-bg-content"><div id class="brz-css-fpcmz brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-d-xs-flex brz-css-lsjsq"><div class="brz-rich-text brz-css-mgrxn" data-custom-id="kxpzmkpkxvcfioadnhzeurdyhrpaxteezgob"><p class="brz-text-lg-center brz-fw-xs-im-500 brz-fw-sm-im-500 brz-fw-lg-500 brz-lh-sm-im-1_2 brz-lh-lg-1_5 brz-fs-sm-im-19 brz-fs-lg-20 brz-ft-google brz-ff-montserrat brz-ls-xs-im-0 brz-ls-sm-im-0 brz-ls-lg-0 brz-fs-xs-18 brz-lh-xs-1_3"><strong style="color: rgb(35, 157, 219);">Jobs at Rise & Offline </strong></p></div></div></div><div id class="brz-css-fpcmz brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-d-xs-flex brz-css-lsjsq"><div class="brz-rich-text brz-css-mgrxn" data-custom-id="bsbwmwtykachbejxajfffwzjgoxpqugmttfq"><p class="brz-fs-lg-15 brz-fs-sm-im-14 brz-ls-lg-0 brz-ls-sm-im-0 brz-ls-xs-im-0 brz-lh-lg-1_5 brz-lh-sm-im-1_2 brz-lh-xs-im-1_2 brz-ff-montserrat brz-ft-google brz-fw-lg-300 brz-fw-sm-im-300 brz-fw-xs-im-300 brz-text-lg-justify brz-fs-xs-14"><span class="brz-cp-color8">LGBTI community member have to often choose between career & authenticity, no more! We bring to you job postings from inclusive workplace who want the amazing you in their teams</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id class="brz-css-fpcmz brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-d-xs-flex brz-css-lsjsq"><div class="brz-rich-text brz-css-mgrxn" data-custom-id="lacqqezxgismmuxpdwhlejmkjhvoiczrsuav"><p class="brz-text-lg-center brz-fs-lg-13 brz-fs-sm-im-12 brz-fs-xs-im-12 brz-lh-lg-1_7 brz-lh-sm-im-1_4 brz-lh-xs-im-1_4 brz-ff-noto_serif brz-ft-google brz-fw-lg-400 brz-fw-sm-im-400 brz-fw-xs-im-400 brz-ls-lg-0_5 brz-ls-sm-im-1 brz-ls-xs-im-1"><sp